      {
        "index": 2,
        "gloss": "style of decorating a traditional Japanese room (esp. a study) in which incense, a pair of vases and a pair of candlesticks are placed on a table in front of a trio of hanging scrolls",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
